鲍姆林德是一位[[加利福尼亞大學柏克萊分校|加利福尼亞大學柏克萊分校]]人类发展学院的[[发展心理学|发展心理学家]]。<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20080513232645/http://ihd.berkeley.edu/baumcv.htm Baumrind CV<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>她由于对[[育兒風格|育兒風格]]的研究<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.devpsy.org/teaching/parent/baumrind_styles.html |title=Diana Baumrind & Parenting Styles<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2007-08-29 |archive-date=2018-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810052443/http://www.devpsy.org/teaching/parent/baumrind_styles.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=There's a brat in my kitchen |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/main.jhtml?xml=/education/2005/10/15/edspoilt15.xml&sSheet=/education/2005/10/15/ixtetop.html |work=[[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2005-10-15 |accessdate=2008-04-07 |location=London |first=Dorothy |last=Wade |archive-date=2006-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060427020936/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/main.jhtml?xml=%2Feducation%2F2005%2F10%2F15%2Fedspoilt15.xml&sSheet=%2Feducation%2F2005%2F10%2F15%2Fixtetop.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和对{{tsl|en|deception (in psychological research)|欺骗 (心理学研究)|心理学研究中的欺骗}}的批评所闻名，特别是对[[米爾格倫實驗|米爾格倫實驗]]的批评。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Baumrind D |year=1964 |title=Some Thoughts on Ethics of Research: After Reading Milgram's "Behavioral Study of Obedience" |journal=American Psychologist |volume=19 |pages=421–423 |url=http://psycnet.apa.org/journals/amp/19/6/421.pdf |doi=10.1037/h0040128 |issue=6 |access-date=2018-08-15 |archive-date=2020-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200409175609/http://psycnet.apa.org/journals/amp/19/6/421.pdf }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Baumrind D |year=1971 |title=Principles of Ethical Conduct in the Treatment of Subjects: Reaction to the Draft Report of the Committee on Ethical Standards in Psychological Research |journal=American Psychologist |volume=26 |pages=887–896 |url=http://psycnet.apa.org/journals/amp/26/10/887.pdf |doi=10.1037/h0